<H3> <TI>   * Aid Contribution From Sweden Increased </TI></H3>
<F P=102>  94EN0194Y Stockholm DAGENS NYHETER in Swedish 11 Jan 94 p 10 </F>
<F P=103> 94EN0194Y </F>
<F P=104>  Stockholm DAGENS NYHETER </F>


<TEXT>
Language: <F P=105> Swedish </F>
Article Type:CSO 

<F P=106> [Unattributed article: "Increased Aid to Bosnia"] </F>
  [Text] (TT)--The needy in Bosnia are going to get more 
Swedish aid. 
  The contribution to the UN refugee organization--the UNHCR 
[UN High Commissioner for Refugees]--is being increased from 40 
million to 275 million kronor. 
  Support for the UN agency for Palestinian refugees--the 
UNWRA 
[UN Relief and Works Agency for Palestine Refugees in the Near 
East]--is being increased from 16 million to 130 million kronor. 

