    -  in CNRS, TGE spending has been virtually constant since 
1990, and its share of total program authorizations has declined 
slightly; 
  -  in CEA, 1992 was marked by a sharp reduction both in program 
authorizations and in TGE-related expenditures. Although the 
ratio does not change for 1993, the figures in both categories 
are somewhat higher. 

